  <brief_title>Ischaemia-réperfusion During the Coronary Surgery With Beating Heart</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Diltiazem and/or N-Acétylcystéine Versus Placebo on hémodynamiques and Biological Repercussions of the Ischaemia-réperfusion During the Coronary Surgery With Beating Heart</official_title>
